Changes in version 1.1.0 (2019-10-29) 
=========================
* Added <pre>uavimg_worldfile</pre> to generate sidecar files for images
* Added cameras argument to <pre>uavimg_info</pre>
* Updated cameras.csv - added Phantom 3 Pro (FC300X)

Changes in version 1.0.0 (2019-04-02) 
=========================
* Modified <pre>uavimg_info</pre> to save the MCP
* Modified <pre>uavimg_report.Rmd</pre> - added param for mcp, OSM base layer 
* Modified <pre>uavimg_report.R</pre> - added argument for Google Maps Static API key, changed default value for <pre>png_map</pre> to FALSE
* Added <pre>stderr=FALSE</pre> to system2() calls in <pre>uavimg_info</pre> to accommodate a bug in R version 3.5.1 and later
* Modified <pre>uavimg_exp</pre>  - added arguments for what to save: ctr, fp, and mcp
* Updated cameras.csv - added Mavic Pro (FC220)

Changes in version 0.9.1 (2018-09-14) 
=========================
* Added custom summary function for drone images metadata collection object, <pre>summary.uavimg_info</pre> 
* Modified <pre>uavimg_report.Rmd</pre> - edited footer

Changes in version 0.9.0 (2018-08-26) 
=========================
* Relatively major update - modified the structure of class uavimg_info to support multiple directories
* Modified function <pre>uavimg_info</pre>, <pre>uavimg_report</pre>, <pre>uavimg_exp</pre>

Changes in version 0.6.4 (2018-06-28) 
=========================
* Updated cameras.csv

Changes in version 0.6.3 (2018-04-06) 
=========================
* Added function <pre>msq2acres</pre>
* Modified function <pre>uavimg_info</pre>: improved error messages if no jpg or tif files found, computed AOI area 
* Modified <pre>uavimg_report.Rmd</pre>: added area 
* Modified function <pre>uavimg_report</pre>: added <pre>png_map</pre> argument

Changes in version 0.6.2 (2018-04-02) 
=========================
* Added MicaSense RedEdge to <em>cameras.csv</em>
* Added function <pre>geo2utm</pre>
* Modified function <pre>uavimg_info</pre>

Changes in version 0.6.1 (2018-03-10) 
=========================
* Modified <pre>uavimg_info</pre> to trap an error when percent forward overlap=0
* Added a <pre>col</pre> argument to <pre>uavimg_report</pre> 

Changes in version 0.6.0 (2018-03-03) 
=========================
* Removed shp_save, shp_dir, and shp_name arguments from <pre>uavimg_info</pre>
* Added function <pre>uavimg_exp</pre>

Changes in version 0.5.0 (2018-03-03) 
=========================
* Renamed package 'uavimg' 
* Added utility functions <pre>cm2in</pre>, <pre>m2ft</pre>
* Renamed function <pre>img_uav_map</pre> to <pre>uavimg_map/pre>
* Added function <pre>uavimg_report</pre>

Version 0.3.0 (2018-01-23) 
=========================
* Initial release

